text: 212929 Satovski (provisional designation 2008 AD112) is a main belt asteroid. It was discovered by Boris Satovski, Timur Kryachko, and Stanislav Korotkiy on January 15, 2008 at the Engelhardt Observatory, Zelenchukskaya Station, near Special Astrophysical Observatory of the Russian Academy of Science, Russia. ==Related pages== *1528 Conrada *1984 Fedynskij == References == Satovski
